All the remaning REM had been reducing itself to raw energy.
For a while, it was simply unbreakable, and the leap seemed too far.
Aeons of bioluminescent 4th layer contacts slowly began to 
further make connections with each point of emanation. What
was the right combination? Leaping it was still beyond reach.
Suddenly, I had the necessary entanglement. The cycles when
reversed on the very own organik core, created unilateral
multi-resolution bursts. That was when it started to come 
closer and closer. zhrzlkl_ remained untouched as a dimension,
propagating its neon seeds in multi-colored patterns and diversions,
awaiting interference to grow. It was my first time ever penetrating it.
Filled with immaterial satisfaction, the flux of existance let itself in.
